    {
      "id": 19,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [2500, 580],
      "size": [450, 260],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 22,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "=== STIXX STORIES LTX-2.3 ANIMATOR ===\n\nSTAGE 1: Z-Image-Turbo Image Gen\n1. Ollama Generate (Node 2): Reads your story script, extracts characters, and outputs the starting frame description.\n2. Load UNET, CLIP, VAE (Nodes 1, 20, 21): Loads the distilled Z-Image-Turbo models.\n3. KSampler Image (Node 8): Generates the starting frame image (Steps: 9, CFG: 1.0, Euler/Simple).\n\nSTAGE 2: LTX-Video 2.3 Video Gen\n1. Load Checkpoint (Node 26): Loads your base ltx-2.3-22b-dev-fp8.safetensors model.\n2. LoraLoaders (Nodes 24 & 25): Sequentially applies the ltx-2.3 distill lora and gemma-3 alignment lora.\n3. EmptyLTXVLatentVideo (Node 14): Creates the video latent canvas (e.g. 768x512, 49 frames).\n4. LTXVImgToVideoConditionOnly (Node 15): Injects the Stage 1 start frame image into the LTX video latent.\n5. KSampler Video (Node 16): Runs LTX video diffusion sampling to animate the frame.\n6. Video Combine (Node 18): Saves the animated video.\n\nNote: Make sure to install the \"ComfyUI-LTXVideo\" custom nodes via the ComfyUI Manager to activate the video generation nodes."
      ]
    },
